ED_Title: Twentieth session of the High-level Committee on South-South Cooperation
ED_DecisionText:
On 14 May 2020, the General Assembly, on the proposal of its President (A/74/L.64),  recalling its resolution 71/318 of 28 August 2017 and its decision 73/553 of 9 May 2019, and noting with concern the situation concerning the coronavirus disease (COVID 19) pandemic,

decided to postpone the twentieth session of the High-level Committee on South-South Cooperation to a later date.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/74/49 (Vol. III)) after editorial review.
